PortSystem 1.0
name		fluxbox
version		0.1.14
description	Lightweight window manager based on Blackbox 0.61.1
long_description	It's based on the Blackbox 0.61.1 code. Fluxbox \
			looks like blackbox and handles styles, colors, \
			window placement and similar thing exactly like \
			blackbox (100% theme/style compability).
maintainers	landonf@opendarwin.org
categories	x11-wm x11
platforms	darwin freebsd
homepage	http://fluxbox.sourceforge.net/
master_sites	http://us.dl.sourceforge.net/fluxbox/ \
		http://eu.dl.sourceforge.net/fluxbox/ \
		ftp://us.dl.sourceforge.net/pub/sourceforge/fluxbox \
		ftp://ftp.kddlabs.co.jp/sourceforge/fluxbox \
		ftp://ftp.chg.ru/pub/sourceforge/fluxbox
checksums	md5 f097b97127461fa3f6f4af4048c75cfc
depends_lib	lib:libX11.6:XFree86 lib:libXext.6:XFree86
